As sectional play enters into its second week, here is a schedule for Friday, Oct. 30 of Indianapolis-area teams in the 2015 IHSAA high school football state tournament: 
All games at 7 p.m. CLASS 6A 
Fishers (6-3) at No. 2 Carmel (8-2) 
Sectional 5 
Ben Davis (5-4) at No. 6 Avon (8-2) 
Sectional 6 
No. 5 Cathedral (7-3) at Lawrence North (3-7) 
Sectional 7 
No. 7 Warren Central (7-3) at Franklin Central/Southport 
Sectional 8
